  </section>

  <!-- Shopping Tips & Strategies -->
  <section id="tips" class="py-12 bg-muted/20 border-b border-border">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-foreground mb-6">Shopee Shopping Tips & Strategies</h2>

      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div class="bg-card border border-border rounded-xl p-6">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mb-2">1. Stack Multiple Vouchers</h3>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground text-sm leading-relaxed">The biggest savings come from stacking: shop voucher + platform voucher + free shipping voucher on a single order. Collect all three types before each sale event. This alone can save you 30-50% on your total order.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-card border border-border rounded-xl p-6">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mb-2">2. Shop During Flash Sale Windows</h3>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground text-sm leading-relaxed">The deepest discounts happen at 12AM (midnight madness), 12PM (lunch rush), 6PM (happy hour), and 9PM (final wave) during sale days. Add items to cart beforehand so you can check out instantly when prices drop.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-card border border-border rounded-xl p-6">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mb-2">3. Use ShopeePay for Extra Cashback</h3>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground text-sm leading-relaxed">ShopeePay users get exclusive vouchers and an extra 10% coins cashback on most purchases during sales. Top up your balance before the sale starts to avoid last-minute issues.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-card border border-border rounded-xl p-6">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mb-2">4. Verify Seller Authenticity</h3>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground text-sm leading-relaxed">Always check for Star Seller or Preferred Seller badges, read buyer reviews with photos, and compare prices across sellers. Our <a href="/blog/shopee-quality-check-guide-before-buying" class="text-brand hover:underline">quality check guide</a> covers this in detail.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-card border border-border rounded-xl p-6">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mb-2">5. Track Sale Events</h3>
