          <p class="font-bold text-foreground mb-2 group-hover:text-brand transition-colors">Earn GCash Online</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">Verified reward offers and prize draws. Earn GCash credits for free.</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/free-gift-cards-philippines" class="group rounded-2xl border border-emerald-200 hover:border-emerald-400 bg-card p-6 transition-all hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:shadow-md">
